title: Strategy & Tactics:USSR vs USA
description:
Year: 2013
Genre: strategy
Developer: Herocraft
Language: English
Average rating: 5,0
Version: 1.0.0
Size: 49M
Publication type: Demo version
Platform: Android 2.3+

Description:

Lead your armies on the battlefields of an alternate reality. After a nuclear attack on Beijing, 
these two titans entered into a deadly fight. Strategy & Tactics: USSR vs USA is a fierce meeting of two frenemies!

Features
- 2 alternative history campaigns (17 missions)
- 3 maps in scenario mode
- Global multiplayer across different smartphones and tablets
- Endlessly replayble Skirmish mode
- Juggle military, economic and scientific development
